  2006 0000048C D0 1A               		BNE		RF_SaveCurrentAsPending
  2007 0000048E AD 0D 00            		LDA		R_RFPacket2
  2008 00000491 CD 14 00            		CMP		R_RFPending2
  2009 00000494 D0 12               		BNE		RF_SaveCurrentAsPending
  2010 00000496 AD 0E 00            		LDA		R_RFPacket3
